nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/seventeen-svt-2ne1-taemin-shinee-asia-concert-tour-hub-composite-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>边界开放，现场音乐回归，<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行</a>音乐巡演如火如荼地进行。包括老牌偶像 2NE1、SEVENTEEN、G​​FRIEND 等在内的明星正在带着新老歌曲环游世界，并很快登陆亚洲。</p><p>虽然其中一些艺术家正在举办自己的头条节目，但其他艺术家则以多流派和仅限韩流的阵容出现在音乐节的阵容中。最近，相关公告层出不穷，因此<em>NME</em>决定帮助提供一份 2024 年和 2025 年亚洲 K-pop 音乐会和音乐节的便捷清单。</p><p>向下滚动查看您最喜欢的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行音乐</a>艺术家是否正在亚洲巡演，并获取有关城市、日期、场地、门票等信息。</p><h2>十七</h2><figure id="attachment_3775644" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3775644" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3775644" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seventeen-follow-again-tour-to-cinemas-concert-film-announcement.jpg" alt="十七再次跟随巡演电影院演唱会影片公布" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seventeen-follow-again-tour-to-cinemas-concert-film-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seventeen-follow-again-tour-to-cinemas-concert-film-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seventeen-follow-again-tour-to-cinemas-concert-film-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/upload