 《鱿鱼游戏》创作者预计第三季将“很快”公布https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-creator-expects-season- Three-to-be-announced-soon-3824914?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=squid-game-creator-expects-第三季即将公布Surej SinghFri, 27 Dec 2024 04:50:18 +0000 NewsTV NewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824914 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这部热门韩剧预计将迎来第三季，也是最后一季</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-creator-expects-season-three-to-be-announced-soon-3824914">《鱿鱼游戏》的创作者预计第三季将“很快”公布，该</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game"><em>鱿鱼游戏》</em></a>第二季已经到来，该剧的创作者已经概述了该剧第三季也是最后一季的发布窗口 - 看看他在下面怎么说。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-3824852">《鱿鱼游戏》第二季评论：Netflix 的生存惊悚片将再次向你伸出触手</a></strong></li></ul><p>备受期待的 Netflix 热门韩国惊悚生存剧集<em>《乌贼游戏》</em>第二季于昨天（12 月 26 日）完整上映。今年早些时候，Netflix 确认该剧将迎来第三季，也是最后一季，预计将于 2025 年推出。</p><p>现在，该剧创作者黄东赫谈到了即将推出的最后一集，包括他认为何时会宣布以及何时发布。</p><p>黄在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/tv/news/squid-game-2-ending-jung-bae-death-explained-mid-credits-scene-season-3-1236255614/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》杂志</em></a>采访时表示：“目前，我所说的任何事情都可能会剧透，所以我要保持谨慎。但我可以说的是，在第二季推出后，我相信我们很快就会宣布第三季的上线日期。”</p><p>至于第三季可能何时首播，黄说：“我可能预计会在明年夏季或秋季左右推出。” </p><figure id="attachment_3824854" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824854" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824854" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama.jpg" alt="鱿鱼游戏第二季回顾" width="2000" height="1271" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824854" class="wp-caption-text"> 《乌贼游戏》第二季中的李政宰。图片来源：Juhan Noh / Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《Squid Game》</em>第二季获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/squid-game-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-3824852">四星评价</a>，Nick Levine 为<em>《NME》</em>撰文：“ <i>《Squid Game</i> 》第三季也是最后一季将于明年推出，说没有明确的解决方案也不算剧透。但最后一集仍然激动人心、令人窒息。当<i>《Squid Game》</i>用触手包围你并用力挤压时，你会喘不过气来。”</p><p>另外，黄东赫在11月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-creator-says-he-made-second-season-for-the-money-3811648">承认他制作第二季的原因是“钱”</a> 。</p><p> “尽管第一季在全球取得了巨大成功，但老实说我并没有赚到多少钱，”黄说。 “因此，制作第二个系列也将有助于弥补第一个系列的成功。而且我还没有完全讲完这个故事。”</p><p>这位编剧兼导演还讨论了他在第一季拍摄期间如何因压力而掉了“八九”颗牙齿，但他承认，鉴于该剧的巨大成功，“我现在感受到的压力要大得多”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-creator-expects-season-three-to-be-announced-soon-3824914">《鱿鱼游戏》的创作者预计第三季将“很快”公布，该</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
