content/uploads/2024/12/doechii@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doechii">Doechii</a>分享了她所描述的新“节目”《<em>拒绝是一条河》</em>的预告片 - 请观看下面的视频。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/doechii-alligator-bites-never-heal-review-3788938">Doechii – “鳄鱼咬伤永远不会愈合”评论：关于斗争和韧性的坦率的声音日记</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（12 月 26 日），这位说唱歌手在社交媒体上分享了<em>《拒绝是一条河</em>》的受<em>家庭事务</em>启发的预告片，该预告片将于 2025 年 1 月 2 日首播。除了预告片，由她本人和其他音乐家主演。</p><p>在预告片中，我们以 90 年代情景喜剧为灵感介绍了该节目的每位演员，尽管没有笑声。 <em>《Denial Is A River》</em>的主演还有 Zack Fox、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/schoolboy-q">ScHoolboy Q</a> 、Rickey Thompson、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teezo-touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/earl-sweatshirt">Earl Sweatshirt</a> （饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brad-pitt">Brad Pitt</a> ）、H Wood、DJ Miss Milan、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-baby-tate">Baby Tate</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sir">SiR</a> 。</p><p>观看下面的预告片。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">否认是一场河流表演| 2025 年 1 月 2 日首播<a href="https://t.co/OM8u2mtGSR">pic.twitter.com/OM8u2mtGSR</a></p><p> — 沼泽公主<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f40a.png" alt="🐊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@officialdoechii） <a href="https://twitter.com/officialdoechii/status/1872412434264416399?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>目前尚不清楚预告片是否暗示了真实的演出或音乐视频，不过 Doechii 指示粉丝在 Instagram 上关注<a href="https://www.instagram.com/denialisarivershow/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@DenialIsARiverShow</a> 。</p><p> “Denial Is A River”是她的混音带“Alligator Bites Never Heal”中最出色的曲目之一。早在 8 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/doechii-alligator-bites-never-heal-review-3788938"><em>NME</em>就给予《Alligator Bites Never Heal》四颗星</a>，并写道：“Doechii 在这张专辑中深入探讨了细节，但到了最后，她找到了安慰和力量，让这张混音带感觉更像是一部声音日记。她的情感历程。”</p><p>自混音带发行以来，这位 Top Dawg Entertainment 的签约者已经达到了多个里程碑，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-announces-alligator-bites-never-heal-2024-world-tour-buy-tickets-3798354">进行一场门票售罄的世界巡演、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-doechii-perform-with-sza-and-tyler-the-creator-at-camp-flog-gnaw-festival-2024-3813489">与 SZA 一起在 Camp Flog Gnaw 的主舞台上表演</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-teases-new-single-im-his-hes-mine-featuring-doechii-3793009">与 Katy Perry</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">Tyler, the Creator</a>合作他们各自的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/katy-perry-143-review-3795535">“143”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tyler-the-creator-chromakopia-review-3807791">“Chromakopia”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820435" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820435" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="Doechii 在 2024 年 Variety Hitmakers 早午餐会上接受“年度嘻哈颠覆者”奖。图片来源：Joe Scarnici/Variety via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/doechii-@-2000x1270-Joe-Scarnici_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3820435" class="wp-caption-text"> Doechii 在 2024 年 Variety Hitmakers 早午餐会上接受“年度嘻哈颠覆者”奖。图片来源：Joe Scarnici/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>随后，Doechii 在 2025 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>上获得四项提名：“Alligator Bites Never Heal”的最佳说唱专辑、“Nissan Altima”的最佳说唱表演、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jt">JT</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaytranda">Kaytranada</a>合作的“Alter Ego (Kaytranada Remix)”的最佳混音录音以及最佳新人奖艺术家。这使她成为第一个在只出一张混音带的情况下就被考虑进入该类别的女性。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">在这里查看明年格莱美奖的所有提名。</a></p><p>她还在<em>《斯蒂芬·科尔伯特深夜秀》</em>中首次<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ggg45-e4oj0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表演</a>了丰富多彩的《Denial Is A River》和《Boiled Peanuts》，向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mf-doom">MF Doom</a> 、嘻哈音乐和黑人女性致敬。</p><p> Doechii 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596">《Nissan Altima》在<em>NME</em> 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲排行榜上排名第 23 位</a>，Seth Pereira 称这首歌是“Top Dawg Entertainment 王位继承人的一场紧张的、炫耀的才华”。</p><p>与此同时，她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>等人一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-radio-one-sound-of-2025-longlist-revealed-rules-change-3814538">进入了 2025 年<em>BBC</em> Sounds 长名单</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-says-paramore-made-a-huge-impression-on-me-and-my-style-3823745">Doechii 谈到帕拉摩尔如何“给我和我的风格留下了深刻的印象”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">海莉·威廉姆斯</a>领衔的乐队是她“第一次接触摇滚乐”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-doechiis-family-matters-inspired-trailer-for-new-show-denial-is-a-river-3824907">受 Doechii 的“家庭事务”启发的“新节目”“Denial Is A River”预告片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看《慢马》明星加里·奥德曼为真正的军情五处讲述一首圣诞诗https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-slow-horses-star-gary-oldman-narrate-a-christmas-poem-for-the-real-mi5-3824903?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=观看慢马明星加里·奥德曼叙述真实的 mi5 的圣诞诗Surej SinghFri, 27 Dec 2024 02:56:59 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3824903 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奥德曼在扮演杰克逊·兰姆时讲述了“圣诞节前夜”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-slow-horses-star-gary-oldman-narrate-a-christmas-poem-for-the-real-mi5-3824903">观看《慢马》明星加里·奥德曼为真正的军情五处讲述圣诞诗的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gary-oldman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/slow-horses"><em>《慢马》</em></a>明星加里·奥德曼为军情五处朗诵了一首圣诞诗——请观看下文。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/slow-horses-season-4-ending-explained-what-happened-frank-3803093">《慢马》第四季结局解释：弗兰克·哈克尼斯出了什么事？</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年圣诞节，军情五处聘请奥德曼为其社交媒体频道讲述当代版的《圣诞节前夜》。这段视频的标题是<em>“军情五处的圣诞故事”</em> ，讲述了几名特工（身份被隐藏）在伦敦总部工作的故事，奥德曼则以<em>“慢马乐队</em>”的杰克逊·兰姆的身份进行旁白。 </p><figure id="attachment_3550861" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3550861" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3550861" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman.jpg" alt="慢马" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Slow_Horses_Oldman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3550861" class="wp-caption-text">加里·奥德曼在《慢马》中饰演杰克逊·兰姆。图片来源：苹果工作室</figcaption></figure><p>奥德曼以兰姆的身份叙述道：“那是圣诞节前一天晚上，泰晤士宫里没有任何生物在动，只有鼠标的点击声。然后是楼梯间的脚步声，然后是闪烁的屏幕，一百台机器的键盘敲击声。熙熙攘攘、熙熙攘攘、热闹非凡，这不是圣诞节诞生的典型场景。”</p><p>他继续说道：“因此，当人们在家里在最后一刻包装礼物时，泰晤士河内的工作人员将改变他们的轮班。五点钟，我们祝您节日快乐。祝大家圣诞快乐，祝大家晚安。”</p><p>军情五处在视频的标题中写道：“今年圣诞节，军情五处决定放弃传统的火鸡，改吃羔羊——杰克逊羔羊。我们认为现在是他把斯劳别墅换成泰晤士别墅的时候了，当他短暂离开他的慢马时，我们请他录制我们所有人给你们所有人的特别圣诞信息。我们的工作人员将在整个节日期间努力确保英国免受国家安全威胁。军情五处的全体人员祝你们圣诞快乐、新年快乐。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DD9UyP